image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nick-cave-kanye-west@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nick-cave-kanye-west@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nick-cave-kanye-west@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nick-cave-kanye-west@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nick-cave-kanye-west@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nick-cave-kanye-west@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）</a>捍卫了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）</a>的音乐的热爱，尽管说唱歌手有争议的反犹太观点 - 请参阅Cave在下面必须说的话。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-unaired-footage-fox-news-anti-semitic-comments-3326989">凭借他的“白人生命问题”的特技，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）终于达到了没有回报的地步？</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月，凯夫（Cave）透露，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-reveals-the-song-he-wants-played-at-his-funeral-3833054">希望坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的“我是上帝”在他的葬礼上扮演</a>。几天后，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）揭开了戏剧性和争议的沙尘暴，包括说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">将他的道歉撤销给犹太人社区，以换取他过去的反犹太言论</a>，然后继续宣布自己为“纳粹”，并写下了“我” Love Hitler”，以及在他的网站上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">在胸部上出售一件白色T恤</a>，上面列为“ HH-01”，可能是对“ Heil Hitler” Chant的引用。</p><p>在坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）烹制的几周争议之后，尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）通过他的<a href="https://www.theredhandfiles.com/kanye-art-artist/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>红色手文件</em>博客</a>回应了粉丝的信件。一个粉丝引用了洞穴的“我是上帝”的选择，他问：“你怎么能听这首歌，而不必看到坎耶已经成为的人的败类？” </p><figure id="attachment_3833058" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833058" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833058" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nick_cave_2025.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nick_cave_2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nick_cave_2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nick_cave_2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nick_cave_2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nick_cave_2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/nick_cave_2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833058" class="wp-caption-text">尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）于2024年11月8日在英国伦敦的O2竞技场举行。 （Matthew Baker/Getty Images的照片）</figcaption></figure><p>尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）回答说，首先表示他不容忍你们有争议的观点：“已经花费了很多时间和精力来解释纳粹主义的邪恶，反犹太主义的危害，为什么出售带有swastikas和swastikas和swastikas和sell的T恤是错误的为什么强迫女友站在格莱美奖的红地毯上是不可接受的。就此而言，似乎我们都可以找到一些共同点。我同意。”</p><p>然后，他指出，他不相信将艺术与艺术家分开：“艺术家与艺术背离艺术的想法是荒谬的。艺术家及其艺术在根本上是交织在一起的，因为艺术是艺术家所表现出的本质。艺术家的作品宣称：“这是我。我在这里。这就是我。但是，艺术的伟大礼物是艺术家挖掘内部混乱并将其转变为崇高的东西的潜力。这就是坎耶所做的。这就是我努力做的事情，这是所有真正艺术家开展的企业。艺术的显着效用在于它胆怯地转化了我们腐败的状态并创造出美丽的东西。”</p><p>后来在信中，凯夫（Cave）分享说，艺术家是“不是我们有缺陷的天性的囚徒，而是可以超越它的囚徒”，“在他的破碎中，坎耶（Kanye）是这个观念的典范，罪恶，超越和天才之间的辫子舞蹈” 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3826400" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3826400" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3826400" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nick-Cave@2000x1270.jpg" alt="尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）和坏种子在2024年表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nick-Cave@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nick-Cave@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nick-Cave@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nick-Cave@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nick-Cave@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nick-Cave@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3826400" class="wp-caption-text">尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）和不良种子在2024年表演。信贷：Katja Ogrin/redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>凯夫（Cave）继续认识到人类“都被破坏，有缺陷和苦难”，凯恩（Cave）也宣布坎耶（Kanye）的观点是“令人讨厌和令人失望的”：“像反犹太主义一样令人作呕 - 可悲的是始终存在，始终越来越多的形式 - 我努力在何处寻求美丽。这样一来，我不愿意使我们最好的人无效，以惩罚更糟的情况。我认为我们不能负担得起这种奢侈品。”</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-wild-god-review-3788381">尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）和坏种子“野神”评论：曾经的黑暗王子让光线</a></strong></li></ul><p>坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）除了他最近的反犹太观点和销售不受欢迎的Swastika T恤外，还引起了更多争议。这位说唱歌手于2月3日与他的Wive Bianca Censori一起参加了格莱美奖，后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-kanye-west-shows-up-with-wife-bianca-censori-who-reveals-shocking-see-through-dress-3833867">没有透露她的外套，露出了透明的连衣裙，下面的裸露身材</a>。后来，他在一个奇怪的发推文中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">声称对妻子的“统治”声明</a>，这也使他说他认为“奴隶制是一种选择”，并表示对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diddy">迪迪</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-brown">克里斯·布朗的支持，</a>并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-voices-support-for-diddy-and-chris-brown-free-puff-3835815">敦促前者在监狱中释放。性虐待指控</a>。</p><p>狂欢看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-x-account-has-been-deactivated-after-bizarre-weekend-rant-3836418">他的X帐户被取消并停用</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">Shopify然后关闭了West的Yeezy网站</a>。后来确认说唱歌手已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dropped-by-talent-agency-following-anti-semitic-posts-3837245">被他的人才机构放弃，</a>他的前任参谋长退出了Yeezy公司。 </p><figure id="attachment_3837246" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837246" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837246" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837246" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特。图片来源：Rich Fury/VF20/Getty图像为虚荣博览会</figcaption></figure><p>除了他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-returns-to-twitter-x-after-ban-and-deletes-racist-posts-3837746">X页再次变得活跃</a>外，周四还看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-says-kanye-wests-site-was-removed-over-fraud-potential-not-swastika-t-shirt-3837621">Shopify指出，由于欺诈的可能性，该艺术家的网站被删除了 - 不是因为它正在出售Swastika T恤</a>。</p><p>自从社交媒体上咆哮以来，你们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">“秃鹰”</a>合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ty-dolla-ign-condemns-hate-speech-following-kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-and-swastika-t-shirt-controversy-3837549">ty dolla $ ign谴责了仇恨言论</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlie-puth-begs-kanye-west-to-stop-promoting-incredibly-dangerous-messages-and-swastika-tee-3837062">查理·普特（Charlie Puthe）恳求韦斯特（Charlie Putgg）停止推广“令人难以置信的危险”信息，</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><em>朋友</em></a>大卫·施温默<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-schwimmer-calls-for-action-against-kanye-west-after-nazi-comments-silence-is-complicity-3836363">（David Schwimmer）则要求采取行动采取行动。说唱歌手</a>是他充满仇恨的“纳粹”帖子的说法，认为“沉默就是同谋”。</p><p>在其他地方，Ye曾被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-sued-for-discrimination-and-accused-of-texting-hail-hitler-to-jewish-yeezy-employee-3837691">一名前Yeezy雇员裁定，并被指控向犹太工作人员发短信给“ Hail Hitler”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3834008" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3834008" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3834008" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-bianca@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3834008" class="wp-caption-text"> Kanye West和Bianca Censori在2025年格莱美奖上。学分：杰夫·克拉维兹（Jeff Kravitz）/电影杂志</figcaption></figure><p>在洞穴选择“我是上帝”作为他的葬礼之歌之前，2020年的音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-hails-kanye-west-as-the-greatest-artist-on-earth-in-new-message-to-fan-2598001">称赞坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）为地球上的“最伟大的艺术家”</a> 。他后来说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-says-kanye-wests-antisemitism-is-deeply-disappointing-3338350">他发现韦斯特据称的反犹太言论“非常令人失望”和“可耻”</a> 。</p><p>他在2022年说：“对我而言，我认为我认为这是可耻的，我认为这是可耻的。经常？这让我非常失望，一段时间以来，我个人很难听坎耶的记录，但与此同时，我在某种程度上更重视输出。”</p><p> “最终，我更重视输出，我知道，随着时间的流逝，我将能够克服这一点，并可以随意再次听Kanye的音乐。他不会永远被困在角色最糟糕的方面，而他创作的音乐是像我们所有音乐一样远离角色最糟糕的方面的旅程。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-defends-fondness-of-kanye-wests-music-despite-rappers-anti-semitic-views-i-endeavour-to-seek-beauty-wherever-it-presents-itself-3838864">尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）的帖子捍卫了坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的音乐，尽管说唱歌手的反犹太主义观点：“我努力在NME</a>上首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
后街男孩在拉斯维加斯球体居住地增加了更多日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-add-more-dates-to-las-vegas-vegas-vegas-vegas-vegas-vegas-sphere-risidency-3838851?utm_source=rss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign=backStreet-boys-add-boys-add-more-日期至拉斯维加斯 - 球形居民Surej SinghTue, 18 Feb 2025 03:33:36 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3838851 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Boyband将是第一个流行音乐，将最新场地的标题为标题</p><p>Backstreet Boys在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-add-more-dates-to-las-vegas-sphere-residency-3838851">在Las Vegas Sphere居住期间增加了更多日期</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/backstreet-boys@2000x1270-696x442.