r classic brand of pop and enlisted the likes of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bjork">Björk</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babyface">Babyface</a> and more for production work.</p><p> The &#39;Bedtime Stories&#39; re-release is the latest announcement from Madonna, who last week <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-shares-new-music-update-calling-it-confessions-part-2-3837834">gave fans an update on her forthcoming new music, sharing that it will be a sequel to her album &#39;Confessions on a Dance Floor&#39;</a> .</p><p> “My Valentine&#39;s Day gift to all my fans is to let you know I&#39;m putting my heart and soul into my new music and I can&#39;t wait to share it with you!! <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f90d.png" alt="🤍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 。 Confessions Part 2,” read her announcement.</p><p> The update comes after Madge <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-shares-footage-from-studio-with-stuart-price-who-wants-to-hear-new-music-in-2025-3822713">revealed that she had been working with Price back in December and has teased new music for 2025</a> .</p><p> Madonna has been working with the hit producer for over two decades now, with him most widely recognised for his contributions to her hit 2005 album &#39;Confessions On A Dance Floor&#39;. Since then he has gone on to work with her on three of her tours, and recently reconnected with her last year as part of <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-pays-tribute-to-friend-who-saved-her-life-after-she-passed-out-on-bathroom-floor-and-woke-up-in-icu-3560359">her acclaimed &#39;Celebration&#39; shows</a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3822723" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822723" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822723" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Madonna-performing.jpg" alt="Madonna performs onstage during the 2019 Billboard Music Awards at MGM Grand Garden Arena on May 1, 2019 in Las Vegas, Nevada. （照片由Ethan Miller/Getty Images摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Madonna-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Madonna-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Madonna-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Madonna-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Madonna-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Madonna-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3822723" class="wp-caption-text"> Madonna performs onstage during the 2019 Billboard Music Awards at MGM Grand Garden Arena on May 1, 2019 in Las Vegas, Nevada. （照片由Ethan Miller/Getty Images摄）</figcaption></figure><p> If 2025 sees a new album from the &#39;Hung Up&#39; hitmaker, it will mark her first LP since 2019&#39;s &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/madonna-madame-x-review-2505126">Madame X</a> &#39;. Since her 14th record was shared, the singer has gone on to embark on a huge world tour, celebrating the hits from throughout her career. The UK dates of her &#39;Celebration&#39; tour featured multiple sold-out stops at The O2 in London – which were given <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/madonna-celebration-tour-review-setlist-3515338">a five-star review by <em>NME</em></a> . It described the opening gig as showcasing “a series of spectacular set-pieces referencing iconic highlights from Madonna&#39;s reign”.</p><p> The tour also marked Madonna working with Price again. Around the time of the two reconnecting, Price said: “When she announced the greatest hits tour I called her just to say, &#39;Congratulations, I think this is a great idea.&#39; And she said, &#39;I was just thinking about you, and I thought you&#39;d be the perfect person to work with on this&#39;,” (via <a href="https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/30772541/madonna-new-music-bizarre/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Sun</em></a> ).</p><p> In other news, Madonna recently<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-praises-sabrina-carpenters-new-vogue-cover-3837310">praised Sabrina Carpenter&#39;s <em>Vogue</em> cover</a> which bears a striking resemblance to the pop icon&#39;s <a href="https://archive.vanityfair.com/article/share/bd86a835-b84c-47a7-bbec-60b9af6ea282" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Vanity Fair</em></a> shoot from 1991.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-is-re-releasing-her-1994-album-bedtime-stories-3838839">Madonna is re-releasing her 1994 album &#39;Bedtime Stories&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
